<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>{{ title_ko }} — 92°C ROASTERY</title>
<meta name="description" content="{{ one_liner|e }}">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/static/img/logo-92black.png">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.min.css">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,500&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --canvas: #FFFFFF; --canvas-warm: #FAF7F2; --canvas-stone: #F2ECE3;
  --ink: #1A1410; --ink-mute: #4A3F36; --ink-soft: #6B5E52;
  --espresso: #6F4E37; --caramel: #C9986A; --copper: #B5703D;
  --line: #E8E0D5; --line-soft: #F0E9DD;
  --font-display: "Cormorant Garamond", "Pretendard", serif;
  --font-body: "Pretendard", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
  --font-mono: "JetBrains Mono", ui-monospace, monospace;
  --r-sm: 6px; --r-md: 12px; --r-pill: 999px;
}
* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body { font-family: var(--font-body); color: var(--ink); background: var(--canvas); font-feature-settings: "kern","ss01","lnum"; line-height: 1.65; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
a { color: var(--copper); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; transition: border-color .2s; }
a:hover { border-bottom-color: var(--copper); }
img { display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; }
.container { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px; }
@media (max-width: 720px) { .container { padding: 0 20px; } }
@media (max-width: 480px) { .container { padding: 0 16px; } }
.site-nav { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); backdrop-filter: saturate(140%) blur(14px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(140%) blur(14px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft); }
.nav-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 16px 32px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
.brand { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; border-bottom: none; }
.brand:hover { border-bottom: none; }
.brand-mark { display: inline-flex; align-items: flex-start; font-family: "Pretendard", sans-serif; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 1; color: inherit; }
.temp-mark { display: flex; flex-direction: column; line-height: .82; margin: 0 .05em 0 .04em; }
.temp-mark .temp-deg { font-size: .42em; letter-spacing: -.04em; }
.temp-mark .temp-c { font-size: .58em; letter-spacing: -.05em; margin-top: -.05em; }
.nav-back { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .75rem; letter-spacing: .18em; color: var(--ink-mute); border-bottom: none; }
.nav-back:hover { color: var(--copper); border-bottom: none; }
.article-hero { padding: 56px 0 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft); }
.eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .72rem; letter-spacing: .28em; color: var(--copper); margin-bottom: 18px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
.eyebrow::before { content: ""; display: inline-block; width: 28px; height: 1px; background: var(--copper); }
.article-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 500; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.2rem); line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 20px; }
.article-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--espresso); font-weight: 600; }
.article-one-liner { font-family: var(--font-display); font-style: italic; font-size: 1.3rem; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--espresso); margin-bottom: 28px; padding-left: 20px; border-left: 3px solid var(--caramel); }
.article-meta { display: flex; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .75rem; letter-spacing: .12em; color: var(--ink-soft); padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line-soft); }
.article-meta span { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
.article-meta span::before { content: "■"; color: var(--caramel); font-size: .55rem; }
.hero-image { margin: 32px 0 0; border-radius: var(--r-md); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--line); }
.hero-image img { width: 100%; }
.article-body { padding: 56px 0 80px; }
.article-footer { padding: 36px 0 56px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line-soft); text-align: center; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .75rem; letter-spacing: .14em; color: var(--ink-soft); }
.article-footer a { color: var(--ink-mute); border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; }
.article-footer a:hover { color: var(--copper); border-bottom-color: var(--copper); }
.source-basis { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 6px 14px; background: rgba(201,152,106,.18); border: 1px solid rgba(181,112,61,.35); border-radius: var(--r-pill); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .72rem; letter-spacing: .12em; color: var(--espresso); font-weight: 500; }
.source-basis.abstract { background: rgba(107,94,82,.1); border-color: rgba(107,94,82,.3); color: var(--ink-soft); }
.links-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 14px; margin-top: 18px; }
.link-pill { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 9px 16px; background: var(--canvas-warm); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--r-pill); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .78rem; letter-spacing: .08em; color: var(--ink-mute); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); transition: border-color .2s, color .2s; }
.link-pill:hover { color: var(--copper); border-color: var(--copper); }

/* ===== EZ: 쉬운 설명 스타일 ===== */
.ez-hero { text-align: center; padding: 8px 0 32px; }
.ez-hero-emoji { font-size: 3.4rem; line-height: 1; }
.ez-hero-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); margin-top: 14px; line-height: 1.3; }
.ez-section { margin-bottom: 52px; }
.ez-section h2 { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
.ez-section h3 { font-size: 1.08rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--espresso); margin: 22px 0 10px; }
.ez-section p { font-size: 1.04rem; line-height: 1.85; color: var(--ink-mute); margin-bottom: 14px; }
.ez-section p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.ez-section ul { padding-left: 22px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.ez-section li { font-size: 1.02rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--ink-mute); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.ez-callout { margin: 14px 0; padding: 14px 18px; background: var(--canvas-warm); border-left: 3px solid var(--caramel); border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.98rem; color: var(--espresso); line-height: 1.75; }
.ez-callout strong { color: var(--copper); }
.ez-findings { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
.ez-findings > li { padding: 18px 22px; margin-bottom: 14px; background: var(--canvas-warm); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; font-size: 1.02rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ink-mute); }
.ez-findings > li strong { color: var(--ink); display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 1.06rem; }
.ez-findings > li.gold { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF8E7, #FFEFCD); border-color: #F0D67A; }
.ez-findings > li.silver { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F6F6F6, #ECECEC); border-color: #C7C7C7; }
.ez-findings > li.bronze { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFEEDD, #FFDCC0); border-color: #E4B07F; }
.ez-findings > li.medal { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F0E6FF, #E1D2FF); border-color: #BDA8E5; }
.ez-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0 8px; font-size: 0.96rem; }
.ez-table th, .ez-table td { padding: 11px 14px; border: 1px solid var(--line); text-align: left; vertical-align: top; }
.ez-table thead th { background: var(--ink); color: #fff; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .02em; }
.ez-table tbody th { background: var(--canvas-warm); color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
.ez-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) td { background: rgba(250, 247, 242, .55); }
.ez-summary { padding: 26px 30px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FAF0E0, #F3E1C5); border-radius: 14px; font-size: 1.13rem; line-height: 1.75; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); border: 1px solid #E5C99B; }
.ez-summary strong { color: var(--espresso); }
.ez-citation { margin-top: 24px; padding: 18px 22px; background: var(--canvas-warm); border-radius: 8px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.7; }
.ez-citation p { margin: 4px 0; }
.ez-chart-card { padding: 22px 24px 18px; background: var(--canvas); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; margin: 16px 0; }
.ez-chart-card .ez-chart-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 14px; }
.ez-bar-row { display: flex; align-items: center; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 0.95rem; gap: 14px; }
.ez-bar-label { width: 180px; flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--ink-mute); font-weight: 500; }
.ez-bar-track { flex: 1; height: 32px; background: var(--canvas-warm); border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; border: 1px solid var(--line); }
.ez-bar-fill { height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--caramel), var(--copper)); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; padding: 0 12px; color: white; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.92rem; min-width: 56px; }
.ez-bar-fill.alt { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6F4E37, #4A3F36); }
.ez-glossary { display: grid; gap: 12px; }
.ez-glossary-item { padding: 16px 20px; background: var(--canvas-warm); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; border-left: 3px solid var(--caramel); }
.ez-glossary-term { font-family: var(--font-display); font-style: italic; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--espresso); margin-bottom: 6px; }
.ez-glossary-def { font-size: 0.98rem; color: var(--ink-mute); line-height: 1.7; }
@media (max-width: 720px) {
  .article-hero { padding: 36px 0 32px; }
  .article-body { padding: 36px 0 56px; }
  .ez-section { margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .ez-section h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .ez-bar-label { width: 100%; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .ez-bar-row { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
  .article-meta { gap: 12px 18px; font-size: .68rem; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="site-nav">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a class="brand" href="/">
      <span class="brand-mark">92<span class="temp-mark"><span class="temp-deg">°</span><span class="temp-c">C</span></span></span>ROASTERY
    </a>
    <a class="nav-back" href="/insight">← INSIGHTS</a>
  </div>
</header>

<article>
  <section class="article-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">— COFFEE INSIGHT · {{ date_display }}</div>
      <h1 class="article-title">{{ title_ko|e }}</h1>
      {% if one_liner %}<p class="article-one-liner">{{ one_liner|e }}</p>{% endif %}
      <div class="article-meta">
        {% if journal %}<span>{{ journal|upper|e }}</span>{% endif %}
        {% if pub_date %}<span>{{ pub_date }}</span>{% endif %}
        {% if doi %}<span>DOI {{ doi|upper|e }}</span>{% endif %}
        {% if all_categories %}<span>{{ all_categories|e }}</span>{% endif %}
      </div>
      {% if hero_image %}
      <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="{{ hero_image }}" alt="{{ title_ko|e }}">
      </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="article-body">
    <div class="container">

      {# 친근 헤더: easy_hero_title 이 있으면 그걸 쓰고, 없으면 one_liner 를 활용 #}
      <div class="ez-hero">
        <div class="ez-hero-emoji">{{ easy_hero_emoji|default('☕') }}</div>
        <div class="ez-hero-title">{{ (easy_hero_title or one_liner or title_ko)|e }}</div>
      </div>

      {# 🤔 무슨 연구야 — summary 또는 easy_intro_paragraphs #}
      <div class="ez-section">
        <h2>🤔 무슨 연구야?</h2>
        {% if easy_intro_paragraphs %}
          {% for p in easy_intro_paragraphs %}<p>{{ p|e }}</p>{% endfor %}
        {% elif summary_paragraphs %}
          {% for p in summary_paragraphs %}<p>{{ p|e }}</p>{% endfor %}
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      {# 🧪 핵심 개념 — easy_concepts 가 있을 때만 #}
      {% if easy_concepts %}
      <div class="ez-section">
        <h2>🧪 핵심 개념 쉽게 풀어보면</h2>
        {% for c in easy_concepts %}
          <h3>{{ c.title|e }}</h3>
          <p>{{ c.body|e }}</p>
          {% if c.analogy %}<div class="ez-callout">💡 {{ c.analogy|e }}</div>{% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      {# 🎯 핵심 발견 — easy_findings 가 있으면 메달 카드, 없으면 key_findings 폴백 #}
      {% if easy_findings or key_findings %}
      <div class="ez-section">
        <h2>🎯 핵심 발견</h2>
        <ul class="ez-findings">
          {% set _medals = ['gold','silver','bronze','medal'] %}
          {% if easy_findings %}
            {% for f in easy_findings %}
              <li class="{{ f.medal|default(_medals[loop.index0 % 4]) }}">
                {% if f.title %}<strong>{{ f.title|e }}</strong>{% endif %}{{ f.body|e }}
              </li>
            {% endfor %}
          {% else %}
            {% for f in key_findings %}
              <li class="{{ _medals[loop.index0 % 4] }}">{{ f|e }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
          {% endif %}
        </ul>
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      {# 📊 차트 — data_charts (가로 막대) #}
      {% if data_charts %}
      <div class="ez-section">
        <h2>📊 숫자로 보기</h2>
        {% for chart in data_charts %}
          {% set _max = chart.values|map('float')|max %}
          <div class="ez-chart-card">
            <div class="ez-chart-title">{{ chart.title|e }}</div>
            {% for v in chart.values %}
              {% set _pct = (v / _max * 100) if _max > 0 else 0 %}
              <div class="ez-bar-row">
                <div class="ez-bar-label">{{ chart.x_labels[loop.index0]|e }}</div>
                <div class="ez-bar-track"><div class="ez-bar-fill" style="width: {{ '%.1f'|format(_pct) }}%;">{{ v }}{{ chart.unit|default('') }}</div></div>
              </div>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      {# 🆚 비교표 — easy_tables #}
      {% if easy_tables %}
      {% for t in easy_tables %}
      <div class="ez-section">
        <h2>{{ t.title|default('🆚 비교')|e }}</h2>
        <table class="ez-table">
          {% if t.headers %}<thead><tr>{% for h in t.headers %}<th>{{ h|e }}</th>{% endfor %}</tr></thead>{% endif %}
          <tbody>
            {% for row in t.rows %}<tr>
              {% for cell in row %}{% if loop.first %}<th>{{ cell|e }}</th>{% else %}<td>{{ cell|e }}</td>{% endif %}{% endfor %}
            </tr>{% endfor %}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
      {% endif %}

      {# 💼 누구한테 의미가 있을까 — implications 객체를 비교표로 #}
      {% if implications %}
      <div class="ez-section">
        <h2>💼 누구한테 의미가 있을까?</h2>
        <table class="ez-table">
          <thead><tr><th>대상</th><th>의미</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            {% for label, body in implications.items() %}
              <tr><th>{{ label|e }}</th><td>{{ body|e }}</td></tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      {# ⚠️ 한계 #}
      {% if limitations %}
      <div class="ez-section">
        <h2>⚠️ 한계도 있어</h2>
        <p>{{ limitations|e }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      {# 💡 한 줄 요약 — easy_summary 우선, 없으면 one_liner #}
      {% if easy_summary or one_liner %}
      <div class="ez-section">
        <div class="ez-summary">💡 <strong>한 줄 요약</strong> — {{ (easy_summary or one_liner)|e }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      {# 📚 원문 정보 #}
      <div class="ez-section">
        <h2>📚 원문 정보</h2>
        <div class="ez-citation">
          {% if title_original %}<p><strong>📄 논문</strong> — {{ title_original|e }}</p>{% endif %}
          {% if journal %}<p><strong>📰 저널</strong> — {{ journal|e }}{% if pub_date %} ({{ pub_date }}){% endif %}</p>{% endif %}
          {% if authors %}<p><strong>👥 저자</strong> — {{ authors|e }}</p>{% endif %}
          {% if doi %}<p><strong>🔗 DOI</strong> — <a href="https://doi.org/{{ doi }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--copper);">{{ doi|e }}</a></p>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="links-row">
          {% if links.doi %}<a class="link-pill" href="{{ links.doi }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOI →</a>{% endif %}
          {% if links.oa_pdf %}<a class="link-pill" href="{{ links.oa_pdf }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OA PDF →</a>{% endif %}
          {% if links.journal_homepage %}<a class="link-pill" href="{{ links.journal_homepage }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">JOURNAL HOMEPAGE →</a>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 18px;">
          {% if source_basis == 'fulltext' %}
          <span class="source-basis">FULL TEXT BASIS</span>
          {% else %}
          <span class="source-basis abstract">ABSTRACT BASIS</span>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>

      {# 📖 어려운 말 풀이 사전 — 항상 마지막에 #}
      {% if glossary %}
      <div class="ez-section">
        <h2>📖 어려운 말 풀이 사전</h2>
        <p>이 글에 나온 어려운 약어와 용어를 한 번에 정리했어. 의미만 알면 본문이 훨씬 쉬워져!</p>
        <div class="ez-glossary">
          {% for g in glossary %}
          <div class="ez-glossary-item">
            <div class="ez-glossary-term">{{ g.term|e }}</div>
            <div class="ez-glossary-def">{{ g.ko|e }}</div>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}

    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="article-footer">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/insight">← BACK TO INSIGHTS</a>
      <span style="margin: 0 16px;">·</span>
      <a href="/">HOME</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</article>

</body>
</html>
